ented and available online. You can find everything about components, tokens, guidelines and principles of OUDS."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"icon finder","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" is also available there to get icons for your projects."}]}],"caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Go to the website and learn things at "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/"}]}],"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-2.png","code":null,"runtimePreview":null,"type":"step"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDS iOS provides also a wiki attached to its GitHub repository. The wiki is a public base of knowledge with plenty of things: available API, technicala architecture, tips about processes, tests, conventions and toolings."}]}],"caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Have a look "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/wiki"},{"type":"text","text":" to discover how OUDS works."}]}],"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-3.png","code":null,"runtimePreview":null,"type":"step"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For technical reasons the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios"},{"type":"text","text":" GitHub repository does not embed the source code of the "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"design system toolbox"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" app. In fact this app and all its snapshots for tests increases a lot the size of the repository."}]}],"caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To get the source code of this showcase app, go to its dedicated GitHub repository at "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios-design-system-toolbox"}]}],"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-4.png","code":null,"runtimePreview":null,"type":"step"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDS is open source, public and uses GitHub as forge. Thus, you will find common things inside the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios"},{"type":"text","text":" GitHub repository."}]}],"caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Do not hesitate to "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/issues"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/discussions"},{"type":"text","text":"!"}]}],"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-5.png","code":null,"runtimePreview":null,"type":"step"}]}],"kind":"tasks"}],"metadata":{"category":"Orange Unified Design System","categoryPathComponent":"Table-Of-Contents-(discovery)","title":"Going further with more resources","role":"project"},"kind":"project","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-6-going-further"},"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesContract/tutorials/OUDSThemesContract/tutorial-discovery-4-use-other-components#Add-basic-components":{"kind":"section","url":"\/tutorials\/oudsthemescontract\/tutorial-discovery-4-use-other-components#Add-basic-components","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Components can be similar to iOS native components, or can also be original and strongly related to Orange Unified Design System needs."}],"type":"section","role":"pseudoSymbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-4-use-other-components#Add-basic-components","title":"Add basic components"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/tutorials/OUDSThemesContract/tutorial-discovery-2-instanci